videos.description: Caitlin Clark finds McKenna Warnock for a 3, but Jailyn Mason quickly answers back by nailing a contested 3 of her own to beat the halftime buzzer.

videos.description: Caitlin Clark is brimming with confidence as she uses a step-back move to knock down a 3 from the Jersey Mike's Arena logo in the face of a defender.
